import React from 'react'
import {  
    Grid, 
    Typography,
    IconButton,
    Card,
    CardContent,
} from "@mui/material";
// icons
import BalconyIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Balcony';
import DoorSlidingIcon from '@mui/icons-material/DoorSliding';
import ArrowCircleRightRoundedIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ArrowCircleRightRounded';
import WindowIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Window';
import CropPortraitIcon from '@mui/icons-material/CropPortrait';
import VillaIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Villa';
// components
import Title from './Title'
import Paragraph from './Paragraph'


const Content = () => {
  return (    
        <Grid container spacing={0}   
        sx={{
            display: 'flex',
            flexDirection: 'row',
            justifyContent: 'center',
            alignItems: 'center',
            py: 10,
            px: 2,
        }}
        >
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={12} md={3}
            component = 'section'
            >
                <Title
                text={
                    'Nossos Serviços'
                }
                textAlign={'center'}
                />

                <Typography 
                variant='h6'
                component='h4' 
                sx = {{
                    fontWeight: '400',
                    paddingTop: 1,
                    textAlign:'center',
                }}
                >
                    Vidros e espelhos em geral
                </Typography>

                <Paragraph 
                text={
                    ' A Vidraçaria Dalton é especializada em serviços de vidraçaria, lidando com uma ampla gama de produtos de vidro, desde portas e janelas até espelhos decorativos e fachadas de vidro. Estamos aqui para atender todas as suas necessidades em vidro.'
                }
                maxWidth = {'75%'}
                /*mx={0}*/
                textAlign={'center'}
                
                

                />
            </Grid>
            
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
                <Card 
                square={ true }
                sx={{
                    minHeight: 200,
                    display: 'flex',
                    flexDirection:'column',
                    justifyContent: 'center',
                    alignItems: 'center',
                    textAlign: 'center',
                    border: '1px solid #ccc',
                }}>
                    <CardContent>
                        <IconButton>
                            <BalconyIcon 
                            fontSize="large"
                            color="secondary" />
                        </IconButton>
                        <Typography 
                        variant="h5" 
                        component="p"
                        sx={{
                            fontWeight: 700,
                            textTransform: 'capitalize',
                        }}
                        >
                        Sacadas
                        </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                </Card>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
                <Card 
                square={ true }
                sx={{ 
                    minHeight: 200,
                    display: 'flex',
                    flexDirection:'column',
                    justifyContent: 'center',
                    alignItems: 'center',
                    textAlign: 'center', 
                    border: '1px solid #ccc'
                }}>
                    <CardContent>
                        <IconButton>
                            <DoorSlidingIcon 
                            fontSize="large"
                            color="secondary" />
                        </IconButton>
                        <Typography 
                        variant="h5" 
                        component="p"
                        sx={{
                            fontWeight: 700,
                            textTransform: 'capitalize',
                        }}
                        >
                        Portas
                        </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                </Card>
            </Grid>

            

            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>    
                <Card 
                square={ true }
                sx={{ 
                    minHeight: 200,
                    display: 'flex',
                    flexDirection:'column',
                    justifyContent: 'center',
                    alignItems: 'center',
                    textAlign: 'center', 
                    border: '1px solid #ccc'
                }}>
                    <CardContent>
                        <IconButton>
                            <WindowIcon
                            fontSize="large"
                            color="secondary" />
                        </IconButton>
                        <Typography 
                        variant="h5" 
                        component="p"
                        sx={{
                            fontWeight: 700,
                            textTransform: 'capitalize',
                        }}
                        >
                        Janelas
                        </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                </Card>
            </Grid>


            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}
            sx={{
                display: {xs: 'none', sm: 'block'},
            }}  
            >
                <Card 
                square={ true }
                sx={{ 
                    boxShadow: 'none',
                    minHeight: 180,
                    display: 'flex',
                    flexDirection:'column',
                    justifyContent: 'center',
                    alignItems: 'center',
                    textAlign: 'center',
                }}>
                    <CardContent>
                        <ArrowCircleRightRoundedIcon
                        fontSize="large"
                        color="secondary" />
                    </CardContent>
                </Card>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
                <Card 
                square={ true }
                sx={{ 
                    minHeight: 200,
                    display: 'flex',
                    flexDirection:'column',
                    justifyContent: 'center',
                    alignItems: 'center',
                    textAlign: 'center',                    
                    border: '1px solid #ccc',
                }}
                >
                    <CardContent>
                        <IconButton>
                            <CropPortraitIcon 
                            fontSize="large"
                            color="secondary" />
                        </IconButton>
                        <Typography 
                        variant="h5" 
                        component="p"
                        sx={{
                            fontWeight: 700,
                            textTransform: 'capitalize',
                        }}
                        >
                        Espelhos
                        </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                </Card>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
                <Card 
                square={ true }
                sx={{ 
                    minHeight: 200,
                    display: 'flex',
                    flexDirection:'column',
                    justifyContent: 'center',
                    alignItems: 'center',
                    textAlign: 'center', 
                    border: '1px solid #ccc',
                }}>
                    <CardContent>
                        <IconButton>
                            <VillaIcon
                            fontSize="large"
                            color="secondary" />
                        </IconButton>
                        <Typography 
                        variant="h5" 
                        component="p"
                        sx={{
                            fontWeight: 700,
                            textTransform: 'capitalize',
                        }}
                        >
                        Fachadas
                        </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                </Card>
            </Grid> 
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
                <Card 
                square={ true }
                sx={{ 
                    minHeight: 200,
                    display: 'flex',
                    flexDirection:'column',
                    justifyContent: 'center',
                    alignItems: 'center',
                    textAlign: 'center', 
                    border: '1px solid #ccc',
                }}>
                    <CardContent>
                        <IconButton>
                            <VillaIcon
                            fontSize="large"
                            color="secondary" />
                        </IconButton>
                        <Typography 
                        variant="h5" 
                        component="p"
                        sx={{
                            fontWeight: 700,
                            textTransform: 'capitalize',
                        }}
                        >
                        Fachadas
                        </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                </Card>
            </Grid> 
        </Grid>
        
    );
}

export default Content
